-- U.K. Foreign Office Minister Calls on Bahrain to Step Up Reform
-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 2012-06-27T17:33:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-27/u-k-foreign-office-minister-calls-on-bahrain-to-step-up-reform.html
U.K. Foreign Office Minister David Howell urged Bahrain to increase the pace of its reform in a
meeting today with Lieutenant General Sheikh Rashid bin Abdullah  Al Khalifa , Bahraini interior minister, the Foreign and
Commonwealth Office said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
